@startuml sequence-customer-registration
title Customer Registration

actor Buyer
participant "web-gateway" as WG
participant "identity-service" as ID
participant "customer-service" as CS
participant "notification-service" as NOTIF
queue "Kafka" as K

== Happy Path ==

Buyer -> WG : POST /api/users/register\n{email, password, fullName}
activate WG

WG -> ID : forward request
activate ID

ID -> ID : validate + hash password \ncreate User (role=CUSTOMER, status=PENDING)\ngenerate verificationToken
ID -> K : identity.customer.registered\n{userId, email, fullName, role, verificationToken}\n[via Outbox]
ID --> WG : 201 Created\n{userId}
deactivate ID

WG --> Buyer : 201 Created
deactivate WG

note right of Buyer
  Buyer nhận response ngay.
  status=PENDING — chưa thể login.
  Không phát token — yêu cầu verify email trước.
  Phần dưới xử lý async.
end note

== Async downstream ==

K -> CS : identity.customer.registered
activate CS
CS -> CS : create CustomerProfile\n(loyaltyBalance=0)
deactivate CS

K -> NOTIF : identity.customer.registered
activate NOTIF
NOTIF -> Buyer : Verification email\n(link kích hoạt chứa verificationToken)
deactivate NOTIF

== Email Verification — Happy Path ==

Buyer -> WG : GET /api/users/verify?token={verificationToken}
activate WG
WG -> ID : forward request
activate ID
ID -> ID : validate token:\n- tồn tại trong verification_tokens\n- chưa hết hạn (TTL 24h)\nset status=ACTIVE\nxóa verification_token
ID --> WG : 200 OK
deactivate ID
WG --> Buyer : 200 OK\n{"message": "Account activated. Please log in."}
deactivate WG

note right of Buyer
  Buyer có thể login qua\nPOST /api/auth/token (oauth2-service).
end note

== Email Verification — Token hết hạn ==

Buyer -> WG : GET /api/users/verify?token={expired token}
activate WG
WG -> ID : forward request
activate ID
ID -> ID : validate token → hết hạn
ID --> WG : 400 TokenExpired
deactivate ID
WG --> Buyer : 400 Bad Request\n{"message": "Verification link expired. Request a new one."}
deactivate WG

== Email Verification — Resend ==

Buyer -> WG : POST /api/users/resend-verification\n{email}
activate WG

note right of WG
  Rate limit: 3 resend/giờ per email.
end note

WG -> ID : forward request
activate ID
ID -> ID : validate:\n- user tồn tại & status=PENDING\n- chưa vượt rate limit\ninvalidate token cũ\ngenerate verificationToken mới (TTL 24h)
ID -> K : identity.user.verification-resent\n{userId, email, verificationToken}\n[via Outbox]
ID --> WG : 200 OK
deactivate ID
WG --> Buyer : 200 OK\n{"message": "Verification email resent"}
deactivate WG

K -> NOTIF : identity.user.verification-resent
activate NOTIF
NOTIF -> Buyer : Verification email (mới)\n(link kích hoạt chứa verificationToken mới)
deactivate NOTIF

note over ID
  Nếu status=ACTIVE hoặc email không tồn tại:\n→ trả về 400 (không tiết lộ thông tin tài khoản).
end note

== Error: Email đã tồn tại ==

Buyer -> WG : POST /api/users/register\n{email đã tồn tại}
activate WG
WG -> ID : forward request
activate ID
ID --> WG : 409 EmailAlreadyExists
deactivate ID
WG --> Buyer : 409 Conflict\n{"message": "Email already exists"}
deactivate WG

note over ID, CS
  Outbox Pattern tại identity-service
  đảm bảo identity.customer.registered không bị mất
  kể cả khi Kafka tạm thời không available.
end note

@enduml
